<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/stuart-anderson> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Stuart Anderson was Vice Chamberlain of HM Household (Government Whip) from 14 November 2023 to 5 July 2024. He was previously Government Whip (Lord Commissioner of HM Treasury) from 16 February 2023 to 14 November 2023 and Assistant Government Whip from 8 July 2022 to 16 February 2023."@en .
